# Tests for ambient.arb — tiller ambient orchestrator-only gate.
# Applied when TILLER_ROLE is unset and the session model is in the reason tier.
# Denied: Edit, Write, NotebookEdit, Bash, apply_patch.
# Allowed read/context: Read, Glob, Grep, view_image, WebFetch, WebSearch,
# ToolSearch/tool_search_tool, MCP resource reads, get_goal.
# No match → deny (combinator default).
#
# Coverage targets: HaltAmbient (kill_switch), AllowRead, AllowAgent,
# AllowTodoWrite, DenyHyphaDaemons, AllowPermittedBash
# (covers readonly + self-uninstall classes), AllowMarkdownAuthoring,
# DenyExecution.

